---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Diseño Web y Desarrollo de Software en Bogotá | DinamyCode"
  description="Desarrollo de software a medida, páginas web de alto impacto y soluciones avanzadas de IA en Bogotá"
>
  <section class="hero-home bg-ink grid-bg overflow-hidden">
    <div class="hero-home__inner">
      <div class="hero-home__content">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-start items-start gap-1 mb-4 reveal">
          <span class="text-dc-red text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[.18em]">Agencia Digital · Bogotá, Colombia</span>
          <span class="w-12 h-px bg-dc-red"></span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-display text-paper leading-none hero-h1">
          DISEÑAMOS EL <span class="text-dc-red">FUTURO</span> DIGITAL.
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-lead text-cyan-300 leading-relaxed">
          Creamos software a medida y sitios web que convierten visitantes en clientes reales.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="https://wa.me/573181252775" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-red action-link bg-dc-red text-white font-semibold">
            Inicia tu proyecto →
          </a>
          <a href="/servicios" class="action-link border border-paper/20 text-paper/70 hover:text-paper hover:border-paper/50 font-medium transition-all duration-300">
            Ver servicios
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-stats" aria-label="Indicadores de DinamyCode">
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <p class="font-display text-dc-yellow">+30</p>
          <span>Proyectos entregados</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <p class="font-display text-dc-yellow">5+</p>
          <span>Años de experiencia</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <p class="font-display text-dc-yellow">100%</p>
          <span>Clientes satisfechos</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section id="nosotros" class="bg-ink relative py-24 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-hidden">

  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-dc-yellow/30 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

    <div class="reveal mb-16">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-dc-yellow text-xs font-semibold tracking-[.22em] uppercase">
        <span class="w-6 h-px bg-dc-yellow"></span>Por qué elegirnos
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-paper mt-3 leading-none text-clamp-heading">
        LO QUE NOS<br>DISTINGUE
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3">

      <div class="ben-card bg-ink-card border border-white/8 rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
        <img src="/assets/svg/Award.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7 mb-4 opacity-75" aria-hidden="true">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-paper tracking-wide mb-2">SEGURIDAD</h3>
        <p class="text-paper/90 text-xs leading-relaxed">Medidas robustas para proteger tu sitio y los datos de tus clientes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card bg-ink-card border border-white/8 rounded-xl p-6 reveal delay-3">
        <img src="/assets/svg/devices.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7 mb-4 opacity-75" aria-hidden="true">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-paper tracking-wide mb-2">RESPONSIVE</h3>
        <p class="text-paper/90 text-xs leading-relaxed">Experiencia perfecta en móvil, tablet y escritorio sin excepciones.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card bg-ink-card border border-white/8 rounded-xl p-6 reveal delay-1">
        <img src="/assets/svg/Calendar.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7 mb-4 opacity-75" aria-hidden="true">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-paper tracking-wide mb-2">SEO</h3>
        <p class="text-paper/90 text-xs leading-relaxed">Aparecer primero en Google no es suerte — es estrategia y técnica.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card bg-ink-card border border-white/8 rounded-xl p-6 reveal delay-4">
        <img src="/assets/svg/Bookmark.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7 mb-4 opacity-75" aria-hidden="true">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-paper tracking-wide mb-2">DISEÑO MODERNO</h3>
        <p class="text-paper/90 text-xs leading-relaxed">Tendencias actuales de diseño que se traducen en más conversiones.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card bg-ink-card border border-white/8 rounded-xl p-6 reveal delay-2">
        <img src="/assets/svg/Camera.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7 mb-4 opacity-75" aria-hidden="true">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-paper tracking-wide mb-2">REDES SOCIALES</h3>
        <p class="text-paper/90 text-xs leading-relaxed">Integración estratégica para maximizar tu presencia online.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card bg-ink-card border border-white/8 rounded-xl p-6 reveal delay-5">
        <img src="/assets/svg/Docs.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7 mb-4 opacity-75" aria-hidden="true">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-paper tracking-wide mb-2">GESTIÓN CMS</h3>
        <p class="text-paper/90 text-xs leading-relaxed">Actualiza tu contenido sin conocimientos técnicos, fácil y rápido.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card bg-ink-card border border-white/8 rounded-xl p-6 reveal delay-6">
        <img src="/assets/svg/Piechart.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7 mb-4 opacity-75" aria-hidden="true">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-paper tracking-wide mb-2">ANALÍTICA</h3>
        <p class="text-paper/90 text-xs leading-relaxed">Datos en tiempo real sobre el comportamiento de tus visitantes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card bg-ink-card border border-white/8 rounded-xl p-6 reveal delay-7">
        <img src="/assets/svg/Download.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7 mb-4 opacity-75" aria-hidden="true">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-paper tracking-wide mb-2">VELOCIDAD</h3>
        <p class="text-paper/90 text-xs leading-relaxed">Sitios optimizados para cargar rápido y escalar en los buscadores.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-home {
    min-height: calc(100svh - 5rem);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: clamp(3rem, 9vw, 7rem) clamp(1rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }

  .hero-home__inner {
    width: min(100%, 1180px);
    margin-inline: auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .hero-home__content {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .hero-h1 {
    max-width: 9.5ch;
    font-size: clamp(3.8rem, 18vw, 8rem);
    letter-spacing: 0;
    overflow-wrap: normal;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    max-width: 34rem;
    margin-block: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.6vw, 1.25rem);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: .85rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .action-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 3.25rem;
    padding: .95rem clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: clamp(.95rem, 2.8vw, 1rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    text-align: center;
    white-space: normal;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: .75rem;
  }

  .hero-stat {
    min-width: 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(244, 243, 238, .1);
    border-radius: .75rem;
    padding: .85rem;
    background: rgba(19, 20, 42, .58);
  }

  .hero-stat p {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 10vw, 4rem);
    line-height: .9;
  }

  .hero-stat span {
    display: block;
    margin-top: .35rem;
    color: rgba(244, 243, 238, .84);
    font-size: clamp(.78rem, 2.5vw, .9rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .hero-home__inner {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(11rem, 15rem);
      align-items: end;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    .hero-home {
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-h1 {
      max-width: 8.4ch;
      font-size: clamp(3.1rem, 16vw, 3.8rem);
    }

    .hero-actions {
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .action-link {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
</style>
